org.hibernate.loader.internal

Class AbstractEntityLoadQueryImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.loader.internal.AbstractLoadQueryImpl
      • org.hibernate.loader.internal.AbstractEntityLoadQueryImpl
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntityLoadQueryImpl

    public abstract class AbstractEntityLoadQueryImpl
extends AbstractLoadQueryImpl
    Represents an entity load query for criteria queries and entity loaders, used for generating SQL. This code is based on the SQL generation code originally in org.hibernate.loader.AbstractEntityJoinWalker.
